   <mods:abstract>Autograph Draft version of Jay's charge to the Grand Jury of the District
            Court of Virginia at Richmond. Nations, as well as individuals must pay their just
            debts. To do so the United States must have revenues, and particular attention should be
            given to evasion of revenue laws. In the present international situation strict
            neutrality on the part of the United States is the only course, and both citizens and
            aliens resident in the United States must abide by this position of the
            government.</mods:abstract>
